3 hours ago 0 Shares Premier League Clubs In Order Of How Full Their Stadiums Have Been So Far This Season Thu Feb 23 2017 18:01:48   18:01:48 GMT+0000 (GMT) Nasir Jabbar Nasir Jabbar in football 
Have you wondered which Premier League grounds are the most full? Well, Talk Sport have compiled a list detailing how full stadiums have been this campaign. 
Though the results may surprise you as the biggest clubs in England fail to land the top spot. Check out the list with Hull City kicking off proceedings: 
20. Hull City - 80.5%
